cement key replacement and issuing access id badges contact with questions regarding security housekeeping the housekeeping contract calls for specific areas to be cleaned at specific intervals throughout the school of medicine if you have questions on what is covered please click the following link to read the coverage specifications there are also schedules for carpet and window cleaning over the course of the year if the work specified is not being done or is not being done to an acceptable level please contact housekeeping at 3 6896 if you have additional housekeeping needs that are not addressed in the standard specifications please fill out an su 13 available at housekeeping and return it to the housekeeping department an account number may be required to pay for the service mail & messenger services contact for change of service or to notify them of dropped service contact information please see the facilites contacts for contact information for each area within facilities management you are here stanford medicine school of medicine office of facilities planning and management navigation for this section office of facilities planning and management home space and assets facilities facilities management capital plan environmental rounds lease information preventive maintenance zone maintenance staff central loading dock featured projects sustainability quick links on line forms contact information location and directions site navigation nav 1 nav 2 nav 2_1 nav 2_2 nav 2_3 nav 3 nav 3_1 nav 3_2 nav 3_3 nav 3_3_1 nav 3_3_2 nav 3_3_3 nav 4 nav 4_1 nav 4_2 nav 4_3 nav 5 nav 5_1 nav 5_2 nav 5_3 nav 6 nav 6_1 nav 6_2 nav 6_3 stanford medicine resources stanford medicine getting care overview find a physician find a clinical care center stanford hospital & clinics lucile packard children's hospital emergency research overview school of medicine news & resources clinical trials departments institutes & centers faculty profiles education & training overview school of m